{
  "stem": "18626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I had a couple of times [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] similar cases [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] during the war time with certain officers like him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because there's a lot of German SS [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who became so devoted because they never lived in with Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They came from-- some-- some of them came from towns where they never saw a Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They saw Jewish only the propaganda school when they became SS soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "How the Jews looks, like rats, with beards dirty, with all different things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So they--they never met Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, Lithuania is a country that the Jewish people are different than other countries, like different than Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Very few Jews-- my grandfather wore a beard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Other couple of Jews wear beards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But most Lithuanish Jews were smoothly shaved and they didn't have beards, and they didn't wear hats.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The same thing like in the United States, people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Clean shaved, cut, nicely dressed, and without hats.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And Germans didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Some of the Germans, the old Germans, SS, they knew because they lived with Jews and they went in schools and in colleges with Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But the young German generation SS, some of the hooligans learned only how a Jew looks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And when they came in and they see clean cut Jews in the ghetto, when we were in the ghetto we were still nicely dressed because we were-- still had our clothes.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were not in striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were 100%, you know, skeletons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we still had our hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were not shaved like in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when those Germans saw how Jews look, so they thought these Jews look almost like we look.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Understand?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
